{"tid":149520,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"荃灣民政處疑派H&M冒牌禮包慶回歸 區議員險中伏","createTime":"2017-03-09T10:49:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-09T14:23:35.000Z","uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a1aa3acd0c9379d1d5ea7109f42d3676d9b8bcff","tid":149520,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T10:49:47.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">荃灣民政處疑派H&amp;M冒牌禮包慶回歸 區議員險中伏<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170309/56405100\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170309%2F56405100&d=MOEBQbH5BhSBv0g7AWUGIW6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=0abb7445\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170309%2F56405100&h=d869a637\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170309/56405100</a></span></strong></div><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170309/large/1489046864_47fc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170309%2Flarge%2F1489046864_47fc.jpg&h=1a69e073&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n荃灣民政事務處日前向荃灣區議會提供慶回歸禮品包，讓區議員派發予區內居民。該區區議員譚凱邦指，在兩日前收到共100份禮品包，昨打開檢查並計劃在今日派發，惟發現禮品包內的「針織人造棉頸巾」，包裝寫著「HsM」字樣，令人聯想是瑞典時裝品牌「H&amp;M」，質疑民政處向市民提供冒牌品或高仿品。<br />\n<br />\n譚凱邦表示，慶回歸禮品包內有頸巾、清潔劑、藥盒、保暖杯、微波爐食物盒及羊毛襪盒等，其中頸巾的包裝印有「HsM」字樣，與品牌「H&amp;M」甚為相似，質地也不甚保暖。他曾到淘寶網站搜尋，發現淘寶亦有出售相同款式的頸巾，每件售人民幣3元，笑言「慶回歸禮品包真係配合主題，用淘寶貨同高仿品，與大陸接軌」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170309/large/1489046865_f094.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170309%2Flarge%2F1489046865_f094.jpg&h=f7f93212&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n譚凱邦提供圖片<br />\n<br />\n他指以往民政處提供的禮品，一向沒有問題，「正正常常，今次我都覺得好神奇」，質疑民政處要求區議員派發冒牌品或高仿品予市民，「區議員無可能派高仿品架嘛，就算唔係侵權」。他稱需確定沒有版權問題才會派發，暫未知荃灣區其他區議員，是否已向市民派發上述禮品包，但指沙田及將軍澳區的新同盟黨友，暫未收到上述禮品包。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170309/large/1489046866_7c46.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170309%2Flarge%2F1489046866_7c46.jpg&h=124a8159&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n譚凱邦提供圖片<br />\n<br />\nH&amp;M官網未見有類似頸巾出售。H&amp;M回覆指，從圖中的頸巾標誌、字體設計及包裝，確認產品並不屬其公司出品，對於有否涉及侵權，現階段不便作出回應。"},{"pid":"a02f5d5c5f4f8ccf493fbaa48a4f6abed6587450","tid":149520,"uid":11001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T10:54:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">蚹</span></span>"},{"pid":"2e3b4834cb65e9aa5ba257cf05a4263f82c43c07","tid":149520,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T13:51:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1883202c8d618d9a5ffec0e6d1584289875e9d40","tid":149520,"uid":42435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T14:17:45.000Z","msg":"高彷即是冒牌"},{"pid":"bd44989d5d7006421fd3a61d97e4a09a434285d6","tid":149520,"uid":56698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T14:20:27.000Z","msg":"依個環保膠真係幾過癮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2da86169ceb3223a7fe7b0656df7fc640e01a97","tid":149520,"uid":5995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T14:21:30.000Z","msg":"9成9高仿等於百分百冒牌"},{"pid":"b1308f2480bc2847924261e7c9882f88c1446ea7","tid":149520,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T14:23:35.000Z","msg":"慶回歸梗係用國貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}